    <item>
      <title>What to Install</title>
      <link>/install/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>/install/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;This guide was written for someone with little or no experience using Hugo or with (CSS/Javascript/HTML).  If you are experienced then go to the &lt;a href=&#34;#tldr&#34;&gt;quick start&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;To be able to make your own cusomtized landing pages quickly and easily you&amp;rsquo;ll need to install minimum of two tools and then grab a copy of the starter respository. The absolute minimum tools you&amp;rsquo;ll need to install are&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;



    
  


&lt;a
target=&#34;_blank&#34;


href=&#34;https://gohugo.io/overview/introduction/&#34;
&gt;


Hugo

&lt;/a&gt;
  - a static site Generator&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&#34;box box--btn-bar&#34;&gt;





    
  


&lt;a


class=&#34;box box--btn btn btn--regular&#34;
href=&#34;https://github.com/spf13/hugo/releases/download/v0.19/hugo_0.19_Windows-64bit.zip&#34;
&gt;
&lt;i class=&#34;btn__icon fa fa-download&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;btn__text&#34;&gt;Hugo for Windows&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;/a&gt;





    
  


&lt;a


class=&#34;box box--btn btn btn--regular&#34;
href=&#34;https://github.com/spf13/hugo/releases/download/v0.19/hugo_0.19_macOS-64bit.zip&#34;
&gt;
&lt;i class=&#34;btn__icon fa fa-download&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;btn__text&#34;&gt;Hugo For Mac&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;/a&gt;





    
  




&lt;a


class=&#34;box box--btn btn btn--regular&#34;
href=&#34;javascript:void( window.open(&#39;https://github.com/spf13/hugo/releases/&#39;, &#39;blank&#39;, &#39;scrollbars=yes, toolbar=no, width=1000 &#39; ))&#34;
&gt;
&lt;i class=&#34;btn__icon fa fa-download&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;btn__text&#34;&gt;Hugo for Linux&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;/a&gt;


&lt;/div&gt;


&lt;p&gt;and&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;



    
  


&lt;a
target=&#34;_blank&#34;


href=&#34;https://atom.io&#34;
&gt;


Atom

&lt;/a&gt;
 a text based editor and the Atom is highly recommended.&lt;/p&gt;





    
  




&lt;a


class=&#34;box box--btn btn btn--regular&#34;
href=&#34;javascript:void( window.open(&#39;https://atom.io&#39;, &#39;blank&#39;, &#39;scrollbars=yes, toolbar=no, width=1000 &#39; ))&#34;
