    <item>
      <title>Quick Start for the Experienced</title>
      <link>/tldr/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>/tldr/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;For those who are Hugo experienced and know what they are doing and are able to &amp;ldquo;figure out&amp;rdquo; the details simply clone the starter repo.  Edit the markdown files in the /sections directory and settings in config.toml.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;If you really know what you are doing and prefer to start from scratch by all means just clone (or submodule) the theme into an existing hugo project&amp;rsquo;s themes folder&lt;/p&gt;

